imdb.plot outline: Philly Love is a comedy about Donald Trump's 2016 Presidential Campaign in Philadelphia. Donald Trump visits historical sites in Philadelphia and ends up with an accidental prostitute in his hotel room. It's starring actors Robert Berlin and Daphne Danielle and is also written and directed by Daphne Danielle.
